@startuml
title 建造者模式 (Builder Pattern) - 房屋建造系統 (優化版)

' --- 樣式設定 ---
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam class {
BackgroundColor White
ArrowColor #d35400
BorderColor #e67e22
}

' --- 產品類別 (Product) ---
class Hourse {
- baise: String
- wall: String
- roofed: String
+ getBaise(): String
+ setBaise(baise: String): void
+ getWall(): String
+ setWall(wall: String): void
+ getRoofed(): String
+ setRoofed(roofed: String): void
}

' --- 抽象建造者 (Abstract Builder) ---
abstract class HourseBuilder {
# hourse: Hourse = new Hourse()
+ {abstract} buildBasic(): void
+ {abstract} buildWalls(): void
+ {abstract} roofed(): void
+ buildHourse(): Hourse
}

' --- 具體建造者 (Concrete Builders) ---
package "具體建造者實作" {
class CommonHourse extends HourseBuilder {
+ buildBasic(): void
+ buildWalls(): void
+ roofed(): void
}

class HighBuilding extends HourseBuilder {
    + buildBasic(): void
    + buildWalls(): void
    + roofed(): void
}


}

' --- 指揮者 (Director) ---
class HourseDirector {
- hourseBuilder: HourseBuilder
+ HourseDirector(hourseBuilder: HourseBuilder)
+ setHourseDirector(hourseBuilder: HourseBuilder): void
+ constructHourse(): Hourse
}

' --- 關係連線 ---
HourseBuilder o-- Hourse : 組合/聚合 (持有產品實例)
HourseDirector o-- HourseBuilder : 聚合 (持有建造者引用)

' --- 說明註解 ---
note top of Hourse : 產品 (Product)：\n最終要建立的複雜物件，\n包含多個組成零件。

note left of HourseBuilder : 抽象建造者：\n定義了建立產品各個零件的介面，\n並持有一個產品物件。

note right of HourseDirector : 指揮者 (Director)：\n負責安排建造的順序（演算法），\n隔離了客戶端與建造過程。

note bottom of HighBuilding : 具體建造者：\n實現抽象介面，\n負責具體的零件生產邏輯\n(例如：高樓層的打地基與普通房不同)。

@enduml